subject: Soccer
Women's World Cup (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Abby Wambach scored in the 55th minute to help the United States beat Trinidad and Tobago, 1-0, in the team’s opening Women’s World Cup qualifying game in Kansas City, Kan.
